          <p><font color="#000000" face="arial,helvetica" size="-1">Dear fellow pezheads,<br>
          I'd like to first apologize for my lack of updates on this section, I'll try to keep it updated more often in the future. All the new pez accessory items have made it hard to keep up. It seems to me that the accessory items are out of control, that pez is out for the money, then again that's what we're all out for. It's really collectors choice of what they buy and do not buy. My opinion is that they overuse the pez-a-saurs. I think they're ugly. They put them on every new accessory. The flashlights, bubblewands, party favors, and pez cars all have them. I think it would be much more fun as a collector to come out with more dispensers than high priced accessory items. I like the $5 Simpsons dispensers I bought way better than the $100 Uncle Sam cookie jar. For that price I'd rather go buy the Uncle Sam dispenser. But just to let you know, I'm working more with the site and I'm going to try to get my pictures put up of all these new items ASAP. I hope you enjoy the updates, thank you to those of you who email me with words of support, it's what keeps the site running.<br>
          Thanks and keep pezzin..<br>
          <br>
          <br>
          Gerad<br>
          Royal Pez Reporter<br>
          gerad@pezheads.net<br>
